        "id": "tile_3_1",
        "title": "Supply Tents",
        "description": "Several tents are arranged in a row on the low grass. Inside are various crates and burlap sacks containing all manner of supplies - food, cloth, rope, survival tools.\nThere's a wooden rack against which is propped several spears and one rusted-looking longsword.\nIt's clear that this is where denizens come to prepare for departure out into the wilds of Aurelion.",
